//-------------------dark mode----------------------------------//
//  some colors don´t change
$colors-darkmode: (
  primary: red,
  secondary: blue,
  tertiary: yellow,
  quaternary: green,
  pink: pink,
  red: red,
  orange: orange,
  yellow: yellow,
  brown: brown,
  green: green,
  cyan: cyan,
  blue: blue,
  purple: purple,
  success: #28a745,
  info: #17a2b8,
  warning: #ffc107,
  danger: #dc3545,
  primary-light: #ff3333,
  primary-dark: #cc0000,
  secondary-light: #3333ff,
  secondary-dark: #0000cc,
  tertiary-light: #ffff33,
  tertiary-dark: #cccc00,
  quaternary-light: #00b300,
  quaternary-dark: #004d00,
  pink-light: #fff3f5,
  pink-dark: #ff8da1,
  red-light: #ff3333,
  red-dark: #cc0000,
  orange-light: #ffb733,
  orange-dark: #cc8400,
  yellow-light: #ffff33,
  yellow-dark: #cccc00,
  brown-light: #cc3636,
  brown-dark: #7c2020,
  green-light: #00b300,
  green-dark: #004d00,
  cyan-light: #33ffff,
  cyan-dark: #00cccc,
  blue-light: #3333ff,
  blue-dark: #0000cc,
  purple-light: #b300b3,
  purple-dark: #4d004d,
  success-light: #34ce57,
  success-dark: #1e7e34,
  info-light: #1fc8e3,
  info-dark: #117a8b,
  warning-light: #ffce3a,
  warning-dark: #d39e00,
  danger-light: #e4606d,
  danger-dark: #bd2130,
  // -----
    white: #f8f9fa,
  gray-light: #dadada,
  gray: #8a8a8a,
  gray-dark: #303030,
  black: #191c1f,
  // -----
    light: #f8f9fa,
  dark: #303030,
);

body.dark-theme {
  background-color: $dark;
  background-color: var(--dark);

  // colors
  @each $key, $value in $colors-darkmode {
    --#{"" +$key}: #{$value};
  }

  & img:not(.dark-theme) {
    opacity: 0.75;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
    &:hover {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
}
